OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms told to stop         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fforce-fitting prepayment   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmeters                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy companies have been asked by the
OL,6, industry regulator Ofgem to suspend the
OL,7, forced installation of prepayment      
OL,8, meters.                                
OL,10,FIt comes after the Times found debt    
OL,11,Fagents for British Gas had broken into 
OL,12,Fvulnerable people's homes to fit       
OL,13,Fmeters.                                
OL,15,FOfgem has asked all suppliers to review
OL,16,Fthe use of court warrants to enter the 
OL,17,Fhomes of customers in arrears.         
OL,19,FIt said firms must get their "house in 
OL,20,Forder".                                
